Output demos/shots/_detail.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 18
Set Width 1920
Set Height 1180
Set Padding 20
Set Margin 0
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set TypingSpeed 30ms

Hide
Type "UNRAGER_DISABLE_KITTY=1 ./target/release/unrager"
Enter
Sleep 7s
Show
Sleep 1s
Type "jj"
Sleep 400ms
Enter
Sleep 4s
Screenshot demos/shots/detail.png
Type "q"
Sleep 300ms
Type "q"
Sleep 200ms
